HEADWORD: Suffisance
<hw>Suf*fi"sance</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F. See
<er>Sufficiency</er>.]</ety> <def>Sufficiency; plenty; abundance;
contentment.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>He could in little thing have <qex>suffisaunce</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Chaucer.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Suffisant</ent>⟦br⟧
